      },
      "text": "## Reservation\n**Aggregate Root** ⭐\n\n### 속성\n- id: Long\n- user: User (FK)\n- showTime: ShowTime (FK)\n- seats: List<ReservationSeat>\n- reservedAt: LocalDateTime\n\n### 메서드\n+ create(...): Reservation 🏭\n+ cancel(): void\n+ getTotalAmount(): BigInteger\n\n### 역할\n결제 완료된 확정 예약",
